      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "WINSUM BELLA (1) was 20 metres away in third at this track over 1680m last start at her first run back from a spell. A nice draw on the front line should ensure a cosy run. Meets a comparable field and she can continue the strong start to the campaign. GOBSMACKED (8) put the writing on the wall two runs ago then improved further last start when he scored by 2.5 metres over 1609m at Hobart. Drawn to enjoy a cosy run but might need things to go his way at some stage. This doesn't look as hard so he is sure to prove tough to beat again. CINCINNATI (4) was responsible for a better effort last time out when runner-up over 1680m at this track. Should run a big race. ONEOFTHELADS (9) must be considered after he finished third over 2200m at this track nine days ago.",
